<collectingCountry box="[2307,2473,2288,2313]" name="Madagascar" pageId="16" pageNumber="707">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
: Province d’Antsiranana, Parc National de la Montagne d’Ambre, 
<quantity box="[2252,2343,2367,2392]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" pageId="16" pageNumber="707" unit="km" value="5.5">5.5 km</quantity>
SWJoffreville (Ambohitra), Station Forestiere des Roussettes, 
<geoCoordinate box="[2029,2202,2438,2471]" degrees="12" minutes="31" pageId="16" pageNumber="707" seconds="37.978">12°31'37.978</geoCoordinate>
